grid.title: RPSLS Editor
grid.author: Cell Society Team 5
grid.description: This configuration shows an RPSLS grid for users to create their own layout. Click on a cell to cycle through its states (Grey = Rock, White = Paper, Yellow = Scissors, Green = Lizard, Red = Spock). First pause the simulation, change cells to the desired values, save the configuration, then reload the configuration. Now you can reset the simulation any time.
